quran[10{c,v,t}:
21,1,"qareeb aa gaya hai logon ke hisaab ka waqt, aur woh hain ke ghaflat mein mun moray hue hain"
21,2,un ke paas jo taaza nasiyaat bhi un ke rab ki taraf se aati hai uss ko bah takalouf suntay hain aur khail mein parre rehtay hain
21,3,"dil un ke ( doosri hi fikron mein ) munhamik hain aur zalim aapas mein sargoshian karte hain ke"" yeh shakhs aakhir tum jaissa aik bashar hi to hai, phir kya tum aankhon dekhte jadu ke phandey mein phas jao ge? """
21,4,"Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne kaha mera rab har uss baat ko jaanta hai jo aasman aur zameen mein ki jaye, woh Sami aur Aleem hai"
21,5,"woh kehte hain"" balkay yeh paragandah khawab hain, balkay yeh iss ki mann gharat hai, balkay yeh shakhs shayar hai warna yeh laaye koi nishani jis terhan puranay zamane ke rasool nishanion ke sath beje gay thay """
21,6,"halan ke inn se pehlay koi bastii bhi, jisay hum ne halaak kya, imaan nah layi, ab kya yeh imaan layein ge ?"
21,7,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay bhi hum ne insanon hi ko rasool bana kar bheja tha jin par hum wahi kya karte thay tum log agar ilm nahi rakhtay to ehley kitaab se pooch lau"
21,8,"unn Rasolo-n ko hum ne koi aisa jism nahi diya tha ke woh khatay nah hon, aur nah woh sada jeeney walay thay"
21,9,"phir dekh lau ke aakhir kaar hum ne un ke sath apne waday poooray kiye, aur inhen aur jis jis ko hum ne chaha bacha liya, aur hadd se guzar jaane walon ko halaak kar diya"
21,10,"logo, hum ne tumhari taraf aik aisi kitaab bhaije hai jis mein tumhara hi zikar hai, kya tum samajte nahi ho ?"
